WEBVTT

00:08.290 --> 00:10.872
This is a special report
from La Plata County, Colorado.

00:11.210 --> 00:13.747
We're reminded of
Jim McKay's words from Munich,

00:13.750 --> 00:16.822
"Our greatest hopes and
our worst fears are seldom realized."

00:16.830 --> 00:18.070
Let's hope it's not the latter

00:18.080 --> 00:20.241
as we wait to hear
the fate of the women, children,

00:20.250 --> 00:22.241
and FBI agents inside the building.

00:24.080 --> 00:26.071
Jim, are you getting this?

00:32.790 --> 00:34.951
_ He comes _
Into my bedroom and lays With me.

00:34.960 --> 00:37.827
He says it's God's will. I'm only 15.

00:37.830 --> 00:40.742
And I'm not the only one.
Please help me.

00:40.750 --> 00:42.490
La Plata County
COLORADO

00:42.500 --> 00:43.990
Tell us about the 911 call.

00:44.000 --> 00:47.959
I believe the "he" that they refer to
is the church's leader, Benjamin Cyrus.

00:47.960 --> 00:50.246
Benjamin Cyrus. No criminal record.

00:50.250 --> 00:53.162
No record at all, really.
What else do you know about him?

00:53.170 --> 00:56.378
It's rumored that he's practicing
polygamy and forced marriages.

00:56.380 --> 00:57.870
Any idea who the caller is?

00:57.880 --> 01:01.702
Uh, Jessica Evanson is the one
who the age fits, but we can't be sure.

01:01.710 --> 01:05.077
So I negotiated interviews
with all the children. It wasn't easy.

01:05.080 --> 01:07.287
Well,
considering their view on outsiders,

01:07.290 --> 01:10.532
it would be best
if you didn't identify us as FBI.

01:10.540 --> 01:15.375
Just use our real names and introduce
us as Child Victim InterVIew experts.

01:41.290 --> 01:44.999
-I'm looking for Mr. Benjamin Cyrus.
-You found him.

01:45.960 --> 01:49.532
I'm Nancy Lunde. We spoke
on the phone regarding the allegation.

01:51.960 --> 01:55.782
"Savages they call us because
our manners differ from theirs."

01:56.210 --> 01:58.701
We didn't come here
to hear you ate scripture, Mr. Cyrus.

01:58.710 --> 02:01.076
Actually, it's Benjamin Franklin.

02:01.710 --> 02:04.952
Emily Prentiss, Spencer Reid.
They're child victim interview experts.

02:04.960 --> 02:10.034
How far from God's word must we
have strayed for there to be the need

02:10.040 --> 02:13.419
to invent a job called
"child victim interview expert."

02:14.460 --> 02:17.372
-We wish we didn't have to be here.
-So do we.

02:17.380 --> 02:19.029
But you are welcome nonetheless.

02:19.040 --> 02:21.747
The children are in the school,
as I indicated.

02:21.750 --> 02:23.069
Thank you.

02:25.290 --> 02:27.372
You're using solar power?

02:27.380 --> 02:30.918
Yeah, we're completely self-sufficient.
Electricity. Food. Water.

02:30.920 --> 02:33.286
Ben Franklin said, "God helps those
that helps themselves."

02:33.290 --> 02:37.408
-You looked surprised.
-No, impressed, actually.

02:37.420 --> 02:39.820
-Thank you.
-For what?

02:40.460 --> 02:41.666
For admitting that.

02:45.330 --> 02:47.958
We go to school, we do our chores

02:47.960 --> 02:52.078
and we treat ourselves and each other
with the respect God demands.

02:52.080 --> 02:54.412
But you've never been off of the ranch?

02:54.420 --> 02:56.411
I brought Jesse here when she was two.

02:56.420 --> 02:58.741
You've talked to
lots of children in your work.

02:58.750 --> 03:01.378
Tell me, are their lives
somehow better than ours?

03:01.380 --> 03:03.075
We devote ourselves to God.

03:03.080 --> 03:05.742
That doesn't mean
we're not devoted to our children.

03:05.750 --> 03:08.787
We are not_ here _
because of your religious beliefs.

03:08.790 --> 03:10.417
Why are you here?

03:10.420 --> 03:16.074
We received a phone call alleging that
an adult male member of your church

03:16.080 --> 03:19.959
was having inappropriate relations
with the younger women here.

03:19.960 --> 03:22.702
-You're talking about Cyrus.
-What makes you say that?

03:22.710 --> 03:24.996
-Jesse, come on... Shh.
-Is it inappropriate

03:25.000 --> 03:27.821
for a husband to share
a bed with his wife?

03:28.710 --> 03:30.871
You're married to Cyrus?

03:30.880 --> 03:34.031
Yes, Cyrus is my husband and a prophet.

03:34.580 --> 03:36.662
It's an honor to bear his children.

03:37.460 --> 03:40.167
Jessica, you're 15 years old.

03:40.170 --> 03:42.821
