03:45.330 --> 03:48.822
Get up. Get up. Come on, stand.
MAN 2: You heard him. Move.

03:50.040 --> 03:51.917
What's going on?

03:51.920 --> 03:55.708
We just got a very
strange phone call from a news reporter.

03:55.710 --> 03:59.328
Is there anything you want to tell me

04:03.040 --> 04:04.325
They don't know.

04:12.710 --> 04:16.282
Chapel, straight ahead.
School to the left.

04:16.290 --> 04:17.416
Team one, hit the school.

04:17.420 --> 04:18.739
Team two, hit the chapel.

04:33.580 --> 04:35.912
State police, we have a warrant!

04:38.380 --> 04:40.245
Clear!
OFFICER 5: Clear!

04:40.250 --> 04:42.992
Team one to team_two.
Be adVIsed, the school is empty.

04:43.000 --> 04:44.376
We have not secured the children.

04:44.380 --> 04:46.575
Hit it again! Hit it again!

04:50.880 --> 04:53.417
We have a hatch.
It's a tunnel.

04:57.540 --> 05:00.668
- What's going on?
-I don't know. Just stay calm.

05:01.250 --> 05:03.912
They knew we were coming. Out! Out!
Move out!

05:05.670 --> 05:06.705
Cover fire!

05:23.120 --> 05:26.578
All right, move quietly,
quickly go to the left.

05:26.580 --> 05:29.208
Everybody stay together.
Children, listen to your parents.

05:29.210 --> 05:31.952
All right, everyone, down to this end.
Have faith.

05:31.960 --> 05:33.109
Where did
all these guns come from?

05:33.120 --> 05:34.951
I don't know.
Garcia checked with the state police.

05:34.960 --> 05:37.246
Stay together. Remain calm.

05:37.250 --> 05:40.162
Everyone remain calm.
There is nothing to fear here.

05:40.170 --> 05:43.412
-This is ridiculous.
-It's okay. Just calm down.

05:43.420 --> 05:46.071
What's going on?
-They're trying to breach the front door.

05:47.250 --> 05:51.664
All right, remain calm, stay quiet.
God will protect you.

05:53.290 --> 05:55.781
We're pinned down.

06:04.380 --> 06:07.668
Cease fire. Cease fire!

06:08.000 --> 06:09.206
Get this door open!

06:10.620 --> 06:13.168
It's the state police.
I'm an officer of the state.

06:13.170 --> 06:14.956
Well, there's nothing we can do right now.

06:14.960 --> 06:17.417
-I can talk to him.
-No, you can't. It's dangerous.

06:17.420 --> 06:20.287
-Nancy. Stop. Nancy.
-Excuse me.

06:22.380 --> 06:25.952
Go away! We have women
and children in here! Please!

06:28.210 --> 06:32.112
Cease fire! Cease fire!

06:32.120 --> 06:34.497
Mr. Cyrus, let me talk to them.

06:42.460 --> 06:44.951
Do not fear,
we are on the side of the righteous.

06:44.960 --> 06:47.246
Where's Lunde?
-It wasn't us.

06:47.250 --> 06:51.573
What? You can't shoot it out
with the cops. You have children here.

06:51.580 --> 06:55.414
I didn't start this.
I'll take the roof, you take the tunnel.

06:56.540 --> 06:58.417
Check your rear. The hatch.

07:16.330 --> 07:17.706
Man down. Man down.

07:18.330 --> 07:19.740
We can't stay here.

07:22.580 --> 07:25.492
Hold your fire! Hold your fire!

07:26.580 --> 07:30.664
We're giving you a chance to pull back.
Please take it.

07:31.080 --> 07:32.741
Bower's hit bad.

07:34.790 --> 07:36.451
Okay. We're pulling back.

07:37.500 --> 07:38.569
Pull back.

07:50.000 --> 07:51.570
They're pulling out,
they're pulling out.

07:51.580 --> 07:52.660
Not for long.

08:26.750 --> 08:29.878
"To follow by faith alone
is to follow blindly." Benjamin Franklin.

08:29.880 --> 08:31.495
B.A.U., Behavioral Analysis Unit
QUANTICO, VIRGINIA

08:35.500 --> 08:37.286
Morgan.
-What's up?

08:37.290 --> 08:38.416
What is reportedly being called

08:38.420 --> 08:41.571
a routine questions-and-answers
meeting by Colorado child services

08:41.580 --> 08:45.323
has turned into a violent and deadly
standoff between Colorado authorities

08:45.330 --> 08:48.072
and a fringe religious group
known as the Separatarian Sect.

08:48.080 --> 08:49.991
-The raid on the sect's compound...-JJ, that's not the ranch

08:50.000 --> 08:51.820
-where Prentiss and Reid are?
-They're still inside.

08:51.830 --> 08:53.206
Hotch!

08:53.210 --> 08:55.747
...Tactical Warrant Service Team
into a forced retreat

08:55.750 --> 08:57.456
after losing a 30-minute gun battle

08:57.460 --> 08:59.109
-with the heavily armed sect.-The TV! Prentiss and Reid.

08:59.120 --> 09:01.202
No one knows for sure
how many people are in5ide.

09:01.210 --> 09:03.667
It is believed at least three
of the child service members

09:03.670 --> 09:05.069
are still trapped within the compound.

09:06.210 --> 09:07.495
One police officer has died
and several others...

09:07.500 --> 09:10.708
All right, that means we're the lead with
Hostage Rescue in support. Let's go.

09:12.380 --> 09:14.575
It turned deadly when
the Colorado state police officers

09:14.580 --> 09:16.070
tried to serve a warrant.

09:16.080 --> 09:17.957
Colorado Attorney General Jim Wells says

09:17.960 --> 09:21.418
the reclusive cult has been the subject
of a six-month weapons investigation.

09:21.420 --> 09:23.490
Six months.
We didn't check?

09:23.500 --> 09:26.788
No, we checked.
I had ATF call Wells.

09:26.790 --> 09:29.327
He told ATF there were
no pending state investigations.

09:29.330 --> 09:30.957
-He lied.
-Why?

09:30.960 --> 09:34.168
Wells is challenging the Governor
in the next election.

09:34.170 --> 09:39.164
He thought that ATF was about to poach
his big election-launching weapons bust.

09:39.170 --> 09:41.536
Now it's clear he didn't know
there were FBI agents there.

09:41.540 --> 09:43.917
He just thought the best time
to serve a state warrant

09:43.920 --> 09:47.458
was when the kids were safe inside
the school being interviewed.

09:47.460 --> 09:48.950
What do we know about the sect?

09:48.960 --> 09:53.078
Liberty Ranch was founded
in 1980 by libertarian Leo Kane.

09:53.080 --> 09:54.957
He created it as a
self-sustaining commune.

09:54.960 --> 09:57.326
Libertarians believe that everyone has
the right to do what they want

09:57.330 --> 09:59.491
as long they aren't infringing
on the rights of others.

09:59.500 --> 10:01.240
But libertarians aren't religious.

10:01.250 --> 10:04.162
Clearly this sect abandoned
libertarian principles.

10:04.170 --> 10:05.819
Benjamin Cyrus, the current leader,

10:05.830 --> 10:08.037
introduced religion eight years ago
when Kane left.

10:08.040 --> 10:09.826
Garcia, what do we got on Cyrus?

10:09.830 --> 10:11.161
Oh, we got bubkes.

10:11.170 --> 10:13.912
It's like the guy never cast a shadow
on the known universe.

10:13.920 --> 10:15.569
However, his predecessor Leo Kane

10:15.580 --> 10:18.378
is doing a 17-year stretch
at Deerfield federal prison.

10:18.380 --> 10:20.610
Apparently libertarians
do not like paying taxes.

10:20.620 --> 10:22.326
17 years for tax evasion?

10:22.330 --> 10:24.207
Oh, no, that would be two years
for tax evasion

10:24.210 --> 10:28.283
and 15 for going after four IRS agents
with a Louisville Slugger.

10:28.290 --> 10:29.530
Let's have Kane brought to the scene.

10:29.540 --> 10:32.498
He's our best chance at finding out
some idea of who we're dealing with.

10:37.460 --> 10:41.032
Miles is dead. He was locking the door
when they shot him.

10:41.040 --> 10:44.168
Laura and Robert were asleep in their bed.
The bullets came through the wall.

10:44.170 --> 10:45.819
What about the baby?

10:45.830 --> 10:47.878
I have her.
She was at the school.

10:49.040 --> 10:52.282
Hello, darling.
It's all going to be all right, honey.

10:52.290 --> 10:57.114
Mommy and Daddy have gone to God,
okay? It's all going to be all right.

10:57.120 --> 10:59.953
-Take her to the temple and pray.
-Okay.

11:02.420 --> 11:04.615
Distribute weapons and ammo.

11:04.620 --> 11:09.114
I prayed this day would never come,
but it has. God will see us through.

11:09.120 --> 11:10.200
Yeah.

11:29.580 --> 11:33.243
Dave, they've left the choice
of negotiators up to me.

11:33.250 --> 11:35.571
I taught most of
the hostage negotiation unit.

11:35.580 --> 11:36.956
You want a recommendation?

11:36.960 --> 11:39.918
-I'm making you the lead negotiator.
-Me?

11:39.920 --> 11:42.536
Why go to the students
when I have the teacher?

11:42.540 --> 11:46.078
Because the teacher is emotionally
involved. So is the agent in command.

11:46.080 --> 11:48.321
I know I am.
This is a unique situation.

11:48.330 --> 11:51.163
We have two agents who could affect
the outcome on the inside.

11:51.170 --> 11:53.877
True, but I can't be objective.
I know them too well.

11:53.880 --> 11:55.529
This outcome depends as much

11:55.540 --> 11:59.078
on our ability to predict the moves
of Prentiss and Reid as Cyrus.

11:59.080 --> 12:01.036
That's why
you're the best man for the job.

12:01.040 --> 12:04.168
Assuming that Reid and Prentiss are
still in a condition to make moves.

12:04.170 --> 12:07.207
I know how bad this is.
That's why I want you doing the talking.

12:09.040 --> 12:10.246
All right.

12:10.250 --> 12:11.535
You're obviously not in charge,

12:11.540 --> 12:12.950
-I can see that.
-I'm sorry, Sir,

12:12.960 --> 12:14.951
I'm under direct orders from the FBI.

12:14.960 --> 12:16.951
I'm the Attorney General of this state.

12:16.960 --> 12:19.030
I demand to know
why I wasn't told that the FBI

12:19.040 --> 12:21.326
was sending undercover agents
into the Separatarian ranch.

12:21.330 --> 12:24.379
The only thing that you're in
a position to demand is a lawyer.

12:24.380 --> 12:27.031
-Who the hell are you?
-I'm Aaron Hotchner, Unit Chief.

12:27.040 --> 12:29.577
I'm the guy who's going to tell the
Attorney General of the United States

12:29.580 --> 12:31.992
whether to charge you
with obstructing a federal investigation

12:32.000 --> 12:33.740
or negligent homicide.

12:33.750 --> 12:37.322
-You can't talk to_ me like that.
-Get off my crime scene.

12:45.540 --> 12:48.202
-Hey, Dan. You know Dave Rossi?
-Sure.

12:48.210 --> 12:49.666
We've been here before, haven't we?

12:49.670 --> 12:52.662
Waco. Ruby Ridge. Freemen standoff.

12:52.670 --> 12:54.706
Let's hope someone
listens to you guys this time.

12:54.710 --> 12:56.996
Oh, they did more than listen.
They put us in charge.

12:57.000 --> 12:58.615
So bring us up to speed.

12:58.620 --> 13:00.497
I've sent the state police packing.

13:00.500 --> 13:03.822
They started this mess, lost a man
in the process. I hope that's okay?

13:03.830 --> 13:06.321
-If you hadn't, we would have.
-Good.

13:06.330 --> 13:08.161
The county sheriffs have had
no run-ins with the sect,

13:08.170 --> 13:11.879
so we're using them as support.
We've had no contact with them so far.

13:11.880 --> 13:14.826
They've got power. Solar. We can
shoot out the panels if you think...

13:14.830 --> 13:16.707
No, no. That's an escalation.

13:16.710 --> 13:19.417
Okay. But that means
they have access to the news.

13:19.420 --> 13:23.163
I'll get JJ to talk to the press.
Are your men ready to be briefed?

13:23.170 --> 13:24.569
Okay, let's go.

13:24.580 --> 13:27.162
We call this the Minimal Loss scenario.

13:27.170 --> 13:32.745
Every person we get out is a life saved.
We won't save them all.

13:32.750 --> 13:36.242
All of us have to be prepared
to accept that situation.

13:38.210 --> 13:42.613
Cults are structured like pyramids.
You got the leader at the top.

13:43.120 --> 13:45.372
Diehard believers beneath.

13:45.380 --> 13:49.783
The biggest group,
the base, the followers.

13:53.000 --> 13:55.912
Women and children.
These are the people we can save.

13:55.920 --> 13:59.378
The Trickle, Flow, Gush strategy is
designed to get base followers out.

13:59.380 --> 14:01.871
At first one or two, then three or four,

14:01.880 --> 14:03.871
then as many as we can,
as fast as we can.

14:03.880 --> 14:07.247
And if at any point
it starts to go bad, we go in.

14:07.250 --> 14:10.378
The leaders are charismatic sociopaths

14:10.380 --> 14:13.827
who target those most susceptible
to their seduction.

14:13.830 --> 14:17.573
They have the ability to see
what each person needs

14:17.580 --> 14:21.209
and then they become that thing.
We have to undermine their perception

14:21.210 --> 14:24.782
that we're an invading army
laying siege to their home.

14:24.790 --> 14:27.418
We'll lose the fatigues.
Rancher's clothes work for you?

14:27.420 --> 14:29.206
Like we did at the Freemen standoff?

14:29.210 --> 14:33.328
Perfect. Anything we can do
to demilitarize this situation.

14:35.040 --> 14:36.166
Hello?

14:36.170 --> 14:37.706
You killed my mommy and daddy.

14:37.710 --> 14:41.703
-Are you going to kill me, too?-No one is going to kill you, honey.

14:41.710 --> 14:44.281
This is Benjamin Cyrus,
who am I talking to?

14:44.290 --> 14:47.828
David Rossi. I'm an FBI agent.
We've sent the state police away.

14:47.830 --> 14:49.741
There's just us and the local sheriff.

14:49.750 --> 14:53.709
All we want to do is resolve this
before anyone else gets hurt.

14:53.710 --> 14:57.077
-Then leave us alone.-I'm afraid we can't do that, Benjamin.

14:57.080 --> 14:59.571
One of the police bled out
on the way to the hospital.

14:59.580 --> 15:02.538
So let's just stop this
before things gets worse.

15:02.540 --> 15:05.748
Please just put down your guns
and come out.

15:05.750 --> 15:08.036
We're believers, Dave.

15:08.040 --> 15:10.611
We believe that God says what
he means and means what he says.

15:10.620 --> 15:13.453
His laws don't depend on
what state you live in.

15:13.460 --> 15:15.280
I have no issue with your beliefs.

15:15.290 --> 15:17.372
You don't, but the state does.

15:17.380 --> 15:19.325
I can't answer for other people.

15:19.330 --> 15:22.879
God will answer for everyone
in the final battle I've foreseen.

15:23.380 --> 15:27.419
That's why I'm here, to make sure
that this is not that battle.

15:27.420 --> 15:29.115
We shall see.

15:29.120 --> 15:32.419
Now the three child services workers...

15:32.420 --> 15:34.911
One of them is dead. It wasn't us.

15:37.380 --> 15:41.373
-I need a name. To inform the family.
-Her name was Nancy Lunde.

15:42.580 --> 15:46.493
Okay. Now, please, Benjamin,
send out your wounded.

15:46.500 --> 15:48.707
I promise you
they'll be well taken care of.

15:49.290 --> 15:51.667
With enough supplies,
we can tend to our own.

15:51.670 --> 15:54.321
Okay. I need a few hours
to put it together.

15:54.330 --> 15:57.322
I'll bring them up myself at first light.

16:00.460 --> 16:01.996
He could take you hostage.

16:02.000 --> 16:04.662
I'm going to confirm the kids,
Prentiss and Reid are okay.

16:04.670 --> 16:06.456
Rossi, at least let me go with you.

16:06.460 --> 16:09.702
No. This is about building trust.
I go alone.

16:09.710 --> 16:12.747
I want the parabolic arc mikes fixed
on every window in that structure.

16:12.750 --> 16:15.116
They won't pick up much.
They have blinds on all the windows.

16:15.120 --> 16:16.246
Unless they're shouting,

16:16.250 --> 16:18.286
the glass won't vibrate enough
for us to get an audio.

16:18.290 --> 16:20.827
Well, if they're not shouting,
these bugs will pick them up.

16:20.830 --> 16:23.572
At least until the batteries die.

16:23.580 --> 16:26.071
How familiar are Agents Prentiss
and Reid with our playbook?

16:26.080 --> 16:28.162
The BAU wrote the CIRG handbook.

16:28.170 --> 16:30.320
They'll know that we're trying
to get ears in there at all times.

16:30.330 --> 16:32.662
Good. Let's hope
they can get these people talking.

16:32.670 --> 16:33.876
They will.

17:17.420 --> 17:20.878
Dave? I'm Ben. Come on in.

17:43.960 --> 17:48.169
The children and our guests.

17:50.920 --> 17:53.320
I'd hoped you'd let me take the children.

17:53.330 --> 17:56.959
No, they're our protection.
I remember Waco. We all do.

17:58.500 --> 18:01.492
-This isn't Waco.
-They stay for now,

18:03.170 --> 18:07.322
while I pray for God's guidance.
Please don't try to force us out.

18:08.290 --> 18:10.747
No one's going to try to force you
out of here. Trust me.

18:10.750 --> 18:13.708
-Trust is _earned.
-It is.

18:17.210 --> 18:21.613
Tell them I'm not crazy. Tell them
I'm just a man living by God's law.

18:21.620 --> 18:22.826
I will.

18:33.540 --> 18:34.575
Prepare the wine.

18:37.000 --> 18:40.993
We are celebrating.
Everyone drinks.

18:41.000 --> 18:42.410
Everyone rejoices,

18:42.420 --> 18:46.379
because today we are one day closer
to being with Him.

18:49.330 --> 18:52.914
Look at Jessica's body language.
The way she looks at him.

18:52.920 --> 18:56.412
She literally worships him.
There's no way she made that 911 call.

18:58.620 --> 19:05.207
